    h1 Privacy Policy
    p Welcome to [Your App Name]!
    p Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our application.

    h2 Information We Collect
    ul
      li Personal Information: Name, email address, phone number (if provided).
      li Usage Data: Information about how you use our app, such as pages visited, features used, and session duration.
      li Device Information: Device type, operating system, and app version.

    h2 How We Use Your Information
    ul
      li Provide and improve our services.
      li Communicate with you about updates, promotions, or important notices.
      li Analyze user behavior to enhance app functionality.

    h2 Sharing Your Information
    ul
      li We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.
      li However, we may share your information:
        ul
          li With service providers who assist us in app operations (e.g., hosting, analytics).
          li When required by law or to protect the rights of our users.

    h2 Data Security
    p We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, no system is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

    h2 Cookies and Tracking Technologies
    p We may use cookies and similar technologies to enhance user experience and analyze app usage. You can disable cookies through your device settings.

    h2 Third-Party Services
    p Our app may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for their privacy practices, so please review their policies.

    h2 Children's Privacy
    p Our app is not intended for users under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children.

    h2 Changes to This Policy
    p We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage you to review the policy periodically.

    h2 Contact Us
    p If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
    ul
      li Email: [your-email@example.com]
      li Phone: [your-phone-number]
